OL,4,CWetherspoons warns price of meals to
OL,5,Crise if VAT goes up
OL,6, Wetherspoons says it will have to put
OL,7, up the price of food in its pubs by
OL,8, around 40p a meal if a VAT cut for the
OL,9, hospitality industry is not extended.
OL,11,FThe tax was slashed on food sold in
OL,12,Fpubs from 20% to 5% during the pandemic
OL,13,Fto help struggling businesses.
OL,15,FBut it is set to return to normal
OL,16,Flevels, in stages, over the next year,
OL,17,Frising to 12.5% in September 2021.
OL,19,FThe chain, which has 860 pubs, said it
OL,20,Fwould "make the entire hospitality
OL,21,Findustry less competitive".
